HEADWORD: Lagopous
<hw>La*go"pous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>lagw`s</grk> a hare + <grk>poy`s</grk>, <grk>podo`s</grk>,
foot.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Having a dense covering of long
hair, like the foot of a hare.</def>⟦br⟧
